Package com.jakezuehlke

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FeeCalculator
    Interface for classes which calculate the fee based on ticket type and hours parked.
    Reader
    Interface for classes which perform reading actions.
    Ticket
    Interface which will be used by TicketFactory to generate an appropriate ticket
    Writer
    Interface for classes which perform writing actions
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalculateHoursParked
    This class accepts two Calendar objects, then converts their HOUR_OF_DAY, MINUTE, and SECOND to a double.
    CheckOutTicket
    This finishes a checked in ticket, unless it's a LOST ticket.
    CloseGarage
    This class contains the methods an administrator would use to close out the application at the end of the day.
    ConsoleStartUp
    This class directs the application's logic flow by utilizing the CheckInConsole's and CheckOutConsole's methods and input String.
    ConsoleWriter
    Implements Writer's writeLine method to output to the console.
    FeeFactory
    Factory Strategy class to find the corresponding FeeCalculator class depending on the ticket type.
    GarageFileReader
    Read a line of input from a file
    GarageFileWriter
    Write a String to a new line in a file.
    GenerateCheckInTime
    Creates a Calendar object of the current day and time.
    GenerateCheckOutTime
    Creates a Calendar object of the current day and time.
    KeyboardReader
    Overwrites Reader's readLine method to prompt and return user's input as a String utilizing Scanner.
    LostTicket
    Implements Ticket to modify generateTicket to return a ParkingBill that is generated by the constructor.
    LostTicketFeeCalc
    Implements FeeCalculator to modify getFee to set the amountDue in ParkingBill for a lost ticket.
    Main
    Main class, simply calls a new ConsoleStartUp instance, then runs its runParkingGarage method.
    ParkingBill
    ParkingBill is an object which represents the physical bill printed out to the customer for payment.
    SpecialEventFeeCalc
    Implements FeeCalculator to modify getFee to set the amountDue in ParkingBill for a special event ticket.
    SpecialEventTicket
    Implements Ticket to modify generateTicket to return a ParkingBill that is generated by the constructor.
    StandardFeeCalc
    Implements FeeCalculator to modify getFee to set the amountDue in ParkingBill for a standard rate ticket.
    StandardTicket
    Implements Ticket to modify generateTicket to return a ParkingBill that is generated by the constructor.
    TicketFactory
    Utilizing the Factory Pattern, generate an appropriate ticket depending on the corresponding TicketType.
    TicketOutput
    Output ParkingBill as a dashboard item or as an invoice.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CheckInConsole
    Enum Singleton for the user's input for the check-in console.
    CheckOutConsole
    Enum Singleton for the user's input for the check-out console.
    Garage
    Enum Singleton for an ArrayList of ParkingBill objects
    TicketType
    Enum for ticket types, also includes LOST for usage on lost tickets.
